trans-unit.source: Represents a text effect that can be applied to text objects.
trans-unit.target: 表示可以应用于文本对象的文本效果。

trans-unit.source: The TextEffect object allows you to add effects, such as animations, to text objects, such as <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>, <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>, and <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> objects.
trans-unit.target: TextEffect 对象允许你将效果，如动画，添加到文本对象，如<xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>， <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>，和<xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>对象。</xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock>
